18 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 68 O.S. 2021, Section 1357.10, is
19 amended to read as follows:
20 Section 1357.10. Clothing or footwear - Exemption of certain
21 sales - Exceptions.
22 A. The sale of an article of clothing or footwear designed to
23 be worn on or about the human body or school supply items shall be
24
